This is a direct port from the given mavern project skeleton code creation.
 
1. Please make sure the files following files are in the same directory before starting.
   - build.xml
   - create.properties
   - playn-getting-started.jar
	
2. Fill in the correct values in the properties file (helpful comments are in the file).

3. Run (default Ant task set to "create-project"):
   > ant

4. Finally ENJOY game development with PlayN.